---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Para seguir aprendiendo -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-center text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Recursos para seguir aprendiendo</h2>
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-6">
        Profundiza en SQL y PostgreSQL con estos recursos gratuitos recomendados.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a href="https://www.postgresql.org/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-blue-400 dark:hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all no-underline group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/40 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Documentacion</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-1 leading-snug">PostgreSQL Docs</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 flex-1">La documentacion oficial de PostgreSQL. La referencia definitiva para cualquier duda.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mt-3 group-hover:underline">postgresql.org →</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.pgexercises.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-violet-400 dark:hover:border-violet-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all no-underline group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-violet-100 dark:bg-violet-900/40 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400">Interactivo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-1 leading-snug">pgExercises</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 flex-1">Ejercicios interactivos de PostgreSQL para practicar queries directamente en el navegador.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 mt-3 group-hover:underline">pgexercises.com →</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://explain.dalibo.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex flex-col bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 hover:border-green-400 dark:hover:border-green-500 hover:shadow-md transition-all no-underline group">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/40 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">Herramienta</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm mb-1 leading-snug">EXPLAIN Visualizer</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 flex-1">Visualiza los planes de ejecucion de tus queries. Ideal para aprender a optimizar.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mt-3 group-hover:underline">explain.dalibo.com →</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Creditos -->
    <div class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 pt-6">
      <p>
        Curso de SQL y PostgreSQL &mdash; Creado por
        <a href="https://github.com/paulovillarroel" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">
          Paulo Villarroel
        </a>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Contenido bajo licencia libre. Comparte y aprende.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>
